From aae718486bd13fb44754bfb19b6630ba3fedb199 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Michael Lerman <mlerman@ironscales.com>
Date: Sat, 16 May 2026 22:32:05 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] fix: cover recording lifecycle exits

Ensure recording state reflects the actual capture lifecycle so stopped, discarded, failed, and auto-ended sessions do not leave the popup stuck active.

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
---
